
The worst airline food is served by carriers American Airlines, United Airlines
and U.S. Airways, while travelers can find the best in-flight meals on such
carriers as Singapore Airlines and Air France,said a recent survey cited by
local media report on Tuesday.

According to a recent survey by Seatguru.com, United Airlines, American Airlines
and U.S. Air lines were also cited for having the least comfortable economy-
class seats, and the rudest flight attendants.

Continental Airlines was the sole U.S. carrier mentioned among the best in terms
of airline food and among the carriers with the most polite attendants was
Southwest Airlines, according to the survey.
